<h3 data-section-id="1yvzzn4" data-start="163" data-end="211">🎯 Best choice for you (based on your goals)</h3>
<p data-start="212" data-end="281">You’re trying to attract clients and build authority quickly, so use:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="mfuxi8" data-start="283" data-end="327">🔵 Navy Blue + White + Gold (Recommended)</h2>
<p data-start="328" data-end="384">This is the safest and most powerful combo for a lawyer.</p>
<ul data-start="386" data-end="500">
<li data-section-id="1tyterh" data-start="386" data-end="433">
<p data-start="388" data-end="433"><strong data-start="388" data-end="411">Primary (dominant):</strong> Navy Blue → #0B1F3A</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fef2q2" data-start="434" data-end="469">
<p data-start="436" data-end="469"><strong data-start="436" data-end="451">Background:</strong> White → #FFFFFF</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p5up8i" data-start="470" data-end="500">
<p data-start="472" data-end="500"><strong data-start="472" data-end="483">Accent:</strong> Gold → #C9A14A</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1wecfh" data-start="502" data-end="523">Why this fits YOU</h3>
<ul data-start="524" data-end="739">
<li data-section-id="k7inf9" data-start="524" data-end="573">
<p data-start="526" data-end="573">Looks <strong data-start="532" data-end="543">premium</strong> → helps justify higher fees</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gndeib" data-start="574" data-end="633">
<p data-start="576" data-end="633">Builds <strong data-start="583" data-end="600">instant trust</strong> (important for legal services)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3t2s5i" data-start="634" data-end="688">
<p data-start="636" data-end="688">Works for both <strong data-start="651" data-end="686">local and international clients</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p3m68c" data-start="689" data-end="739">
<p data-start="691" data-end="739">Doesn’t look like a “beginner freelancer” site</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="741" data-end="744">
<h2 data-section-id="x4ro0" data-start="746" data-end="786">💡 How to actually use it (important)</h2>
<ul data-start="788" data-end="958">
<li data-section-id="16v4509" data-start="788" data-end="820">
<p data-start="790" data-end="820"><strong data-start="790" data-end="808">Header/Footer:</strong> Navy Blue</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fxyv06" data-start="821" data-end="850">
<p data-start="823" data-end="850"><strong data-start="823" data-end="832">Text:</strong> Black/Dark Gray</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m3gnug" data-start="851" data-end="913">
<p data-start="853" data-end="913"><strong data-start="853" data-end="865">Buttons:</strong> Gold (e.g. “Contact Me”, “Book Consultation”)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1eoq9pp" data-start="914" data-end="958">
<p data-start="916" data-end="958"><strong data-start="916" data-end="931">Background:</strong> White or very light gray</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="960" data-end="1027">👉 Keep it clean. Law websites win with simplicity, not creativity.</p>
<hr data-start="1029" data-end="1032">
<h2 data-section-id="nriqlb" data-start="1034" data-end="1087">⚖️ If you still want something modern (2nd option)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="14pyzow" data-start="1089" data-end="1126">🔵 Deep Blue + Light Gray + White</h3>
<ul data-start="1127" data-end="1184">
<li data-section-id="xkxk1k" data-start="1127" data-end="1145">
<p data-start="1129" data-end="1145">Blue → #1E3A8A</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="b74air" data-start="1146" data-end="1164">
<p data-start="1148" data-end="1164">Gray → #F3F4F6</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17o9y1q" data-start="1165" data-end="1184">
<p data-start="1167" data-end="1184">White → #FFFFFF</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1186" data-end="1255">👉 This feels more <strong data-start="1205" data-end="1232">modern and approachable</strong> but still professional</p>
<hr data-start="1257" data-end="1260">
<h2 data-section-id="1md37sp" data-start="1262" data-end="1305">🚫 What I’d avoid (for you specifically)</h2>
<ul data-start="1306" data-end="1429">
<li data-section-id="qvf8rs" data-start="1306" data-end="1356">
<p data-start="1308" data-end="1356">Blue + Teal + Orange → looks like tech startup</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="t89w66" data-start="1357" data-end="1390">
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1390">Too many colors → kills trust</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ucst95" data-start="1391" data-end="1429">
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1429">Bright colors → reduce seriousness</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1431" data-end="1434">
<h2 data-section-id="116xme7" data-start="1436" data-end="1454">Straight advice</h2>
<p data-start="1455" data-end="1475">If you’re trying to:</p>
<ul data-start="1476" data-end="1559">
<li data-section-id="mkkgtr" data-start="1476" data-end="1532">
<p data-start="1478" data-end="1532">Get <strong data-start="1482" data-end="1532">clients from LinkedIn / Fiverr / cold outreach</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pbcxu7" data-start="1533" data-end="1559">
<p data-start="1535" data-end="1559">Build <strong data-start="1541" data-end="1559">authority fast</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1561" data-end="1610">👉 Go with <strong data-start="1572" data-end="1595">Navy + White + Gold</strong>. Don’t gamble.</p>
<hr data-start="1612" data-end="1615">
<p data-start="1617" data-end="1636">If you want, I can:</p>
<ul data-start="1637" data-end="1822" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="t7rqgd" data-start="1637" data-end="1706">
<p data-start="1639" data-end="1706">Design your <strong data-start="1651" data-end="1704">full website layout (hero section, sections, CTA)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5ujs7v" data-start="1707" data-end="1741">
<p data-start="1709" data-end="1741">Suggest <strong data-start="1717" data-end="1739">fonts + logo style</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18r0788" data-start="1742" data-end="1822" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1744" data-end="1822" data-is-last-node="">Or build a <strong data-start="1755" data-end="1822" data-is-last-node="">complete branding kit for “Danyal Durrani | Law / Skip Tracing”</strong></p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-c