<p data-start="47" data-end="94">👉 <strong data-start="50" data-end="94">Use Deep Navy Blue + White + Subtle Gold</strong></p>
<p data-start="96" data-end="163">Not trendy. Not experimental. Just <strong data-start="131" data-end="162">high-trust, high-conversion</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="165" data-end="168">
<h2 data-section-id="1egsjx0" data-start="170" data-end="197">🎯 Why this wins in 2026</h2>
<ul data-start="198" data-end="364">
<li data-section-id="11t52d7" data-start="198" data-end="242">
<p data-start="200" data-end="242">People judge legal services in <strong data-start="231" data-end="242">seconds</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jo6ysv" data-start="243" data-end="297">
<p data-start="245" data-end="297">Clients want <strong data-start="258" data-end="281">authority + clarity</strong>, not creativity</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m7v0rc" data-start="298" data-end="364">
<p data-start="300" data-end="364">Most high-performing law firms still stick close to this palette</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="366" data-end="369">
<h2 data-section-id="1sjpvg9" data-start="371" data-end="403">✅ Your exact setup (use this)</h2>
<ul data-start="404" data-end="568">
<li data-section-id="1fg9h12" data-start="404" data-end="450">
<p data-start="406" data-end="450"><strong data-start="406" data-end="426">Primary (brand):</strong> Deep Navy → <code data-start="439" data-end="448">#0B1F3A</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sb7xey" data-start="451" data-end="488">
<p data-start="453" data-end="488"><strong data-start="453" data-end="468">Background:</strong> White → <code data-start="477" data-end="486">#FFFFFF</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="y9y675" data-start="489" data-end="532">
<p data-start="491" data-end="532"><strong data-start="491" data-end="513">Accent (CTA only):</strong> Gold → <code data-start="521" data-end="530">#C9A14A</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mw2j3r" data-start="533" data-end="568">
<p data-start="535" data-end="568"><strong data-start="535" data-end="544">Text:</strong> Dark Gray → <code data-start="557" data-end="566">#1F2937</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="570" data-end="573">
<h2 data-section-id="1w30oj6" data-start="575" data-end="599">⚖️ How it should feel</h2>
<ul data-start="600" data-end="652">
<li data-section-id="8yak3x" data-start="600" data-end="609">
<p data-start="602" data-end="609">Clean</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n617mm" data-start="610" data-end="623">
<p data-start="612" data-end="623">Confident</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oi6eib" data-start="624" data-end="635">
<p data-start="626" data-end="635">Premium</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ukzxzj" data-start="636" data-end="652">
<p data-start="638" data-end="652">Easy to read</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="654" data-end="657">
<h2 data-section-id="18itowj" data-start="659" data-end="689">🚫 What to skip (seriously)</h2>
<ul data-start="690" data-end="824">
<li data-section-id="1n0ty34" data-start="690" data-end="740">
<p data-start="692" data-end="740">Blue + Teal + Orange → looks like SaaS company</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3q8zif" data-start="741" data-end="781">
<p data-start="743" data-end="781">Too colorful → kills trust instantly</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1genfwj" data-start="782" data-end="824">
<p data-start="784" data-end="824">Fancy gradients → cheapens legal brand</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="826" data-end="829">
<h2 data-section-id="1gdl447" data-start="831" data-end="859">🧠 Real-world positioning</h2>
<ul data-start="860" data-end="974">
<li data-section-id="t1w27" data-start="860" data-end="917">
<p data-start="862" data-end="917">Want <strong data-start="867" data-end="901">serious clients / higher fees?</strong> → Navy + Gold</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q2q602" data-start="918" data-end="974">
<p data-start="920" data-end="974">Want <strong data-start="925" data-end="956">cheap gigs / beginner vibe?</strong> → flashy colors</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="976" data-end="979">
<p data-start="981" data-end="1086">If you want to stand out, don’t try to look different—<br data-start="1035" data-end="1038">
👉 <strong data-start="1041" data-end="1086">look more trustworthy than everyone else.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1088" data-end="1091">
