<p data-start="1156" data-end="1198">Suggest <strong data-start="1164" data-end="1198">font pairings (very important)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1msustn" data-start="1199" data-end="1253" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1201" data-end="1253" data-is-last-node="">Or build a <strong data-start="1212" data-end="1253" data-is-last-node="">complete brand identity for your name</strong></p>
</li>
