<hr data-start="1539" data-end="1542">
<h2 data-section-id="4l7l7o" data-start="1544" data-end="1588">✅ 4. Add Core Sections (minimum required)</h2>
<p data-start="1590" data-end="1613">You already referenced:</p>
<ul data-start="1614" data-end="1664">
<li data-section-id="mw9zia" data-start="1614" data-end="1631">
<p data-start="1616" data-end="1631"><code data-start="1616" data-end="1631">.service-card</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zx8bk6" data-start="1632" data-end="1648">
<p data-start="1634" data-end="1648"><code data-start="1634" data-end="1648">.team-member</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r5m2er" data-start="1649" data-end="1664">
<p data-start="1651" data-end="1664"><code data-start="1651" data-end="1664">.about-item</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1666" data-end="1713">Now actually <strong data-start="1679" data-end="1712">create those sections in HTML</strong>:</p>
