<p data-start="139" data-end="172">Here’s exactly what to do next 👇</p>
<hr data-start="174" data-end="177">
<h2 data-section-id="bh0n3g" data-start="179" data-end="241">🚀 OPTION 1 (BEST): Run your website locally on your laptop</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="18p7c2q" data-start="243" data-end="277">✅ Step 1: Download the project</h3>
<ul data-start="278" data-end="385">
<li data-section-id="d4bjr2" data-start="278" data-end="338">
<p data-start="280" data-end="338">Go to your repo on <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xahs6m" data-start="339" data-end="372">
<p data-start="341" data-end="372">Click <strong data-start="347" data-end="370">Code → Download ZIP</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x5lz7c" data-start="373" data-end="385">
<p data-start="375" data-end="385">Extract it</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="387" data-end="390">
<h3 data-section-id="113h8p6" data-start="392" data-end="454">✅ Step 2: Open it in <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Visual Studio Code</span></span></h3>
<ul data-start="455" data-end="545">
<li data-section-id="1qmaxo4" data-start="455" data-end="471">
<p data-start="457" data-end="471">Open VS Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="141eggg" data-start="472" data-end="504">
<p data-start="474" data-end="504">Click <strong data-start="480" data-end="502">File → Open Folder</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="w6nd26" data-start="505" data-end="545">
<p data-start="507" data-end="545">Select your extracted project folder</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="547" data-end="550">
<h3 data-section-id="uyy08d" data-start="552" data-end="597">✅ Step 3: Install Live Server (important)</h3>
<ul data-start="598" data-end="685">
<li data-section-id="8z7p3z" data-start="598" data-end="625">
<p data-start="600" data-end="625">In VS Code → Extensions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fllr10" data-start="626" data-end="670">
<p data-start="628" data-end="670">Search: <strong data-start="636" data-end="651">Live Server</strong> (by Ritwick Dey)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uvp0us" data-start="671" data-end="685">
<p data-start="673" data-end="685">Install it</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="687" data-end="690">
<h3 data-section-id="uum57g" data-start="692" data-end="722">✅ Step 4: Run your website</h3>
<ul data-start="723" data-end="786">
<li data-section-id="a37hsh" data-start="723" data-end="744">
<p data-start="725" data-end="744">Open <code data-start="730" data-end="742">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="60hcak" data-start="745" data-end="786">
<p data-start="747" data-end="786">Right-click → <strong data-start="761" data-end="786">Open with Live Server</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="788" data-end="830">👉 Your website will open in browser like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="831" data-end="860"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://127.0.0.1:5500</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="862" data-end="896">Now you can edit freely—no limits.</p>
<hr data-start="898" data-end="901">
<h2 data-section-id="1l3qokc" data-start="903" data-end="956">🌐 OPTION 2: Put your site LIVE (no coding needed)</h2>
<p data-start="958" data-end="979">Use <strong data-start="962" data-end="978">GitHub Pages</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="onac65" data-start="981" data-end="991">Steps:</h3>
<ol data-start="992" data-end="1185">
<li data-section-id="17pl34c" data-start="992" data-end="1053">
<p data-start="995" data-end="1053">Go to your repo on <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9fsitu" data-start="1054" data-end="1077">
<p data-start="1057" data-end="1077">Click <strong data-start="1063" data-end="1075">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12ddzpn" data-start="1078" data-end="1098">
<p data-start="1081" data-end="1098">Go to <strong data-start="1087" data-end="1096">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13kdsob" data-start="1099" data-end="1167">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1126">Under “Source” → select:</p>
<ul data-start="1130" data-end="1167">
<li data-section-id="15hmgtp" data-start="1130" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1132" data-end="1146">Branch: <code data-start="1140" data-end="1146">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cgd099" data-start="1150" data-end="1167">
<p data-start="1152" data-end="1167">Folder: <code data-start="1160" data-end="1167">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2lh6q9" data-start="1168" data-end="1185">
<p data-start="1171" data-end="1185">Click <strong data-start="1177" data-end="1185">Save</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1213">👉 You’ll get a link like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1214" data-end="1261"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://yourname.github.io/project-name</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1263" data-end="1266">
<h2 data-section-id="1etma1r" data-start="1268" data-end="1296">⚠️ Why Codespaces stopped</h2>
<ul data-start="1297" data-end="1357">
<li data-section-id="1txbbm" data-start="1297" data-end="1330">
<p data-start="1299" data-end="1330">Free plan has <strong data-start="1313" data-end="1330">limited hours</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1euziru" data-start="1331" data-end="1357">
<p data-start="1333" data-end="1357">Once finished → it locks</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1402">👉 Solution = work locally (best long-term)</p>
<hr data-start="1404" data-end="1407">
<h2 data-section-id="1kfl65n" data-start="1409" data-end="1443">🎯 What you should do RIGHT NOW</h2>
<ol data-start="1444" data-end="1542">
<li data-section-id="7au0fh" data-start="1444" data-end="1461">
<p data-start="1447" data-end="1461">Download ZIP</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y3xkyq" data-start="1462" data-end="1482">
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1482">Open in VS Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mixpxc" data-start="1483" data-end="1508">
<p data-start="1486" data-end="1508">Run with Live Server</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tvdgrl" data-start="1509" data-end="1542">
<p data-start="1512" data-end="1542">Continue editing your design</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1544" data-end="1547">
<h2 data-section-id="1tu4d26" data-start="1549" data-end="1590">💡 Pro move (important for your goals)</h2>
<p data-start="1591" data-end="1609">Once it’s working:</p>
<ul data-start="1611" data-end="1740">
<li data-section-id="1oxavlv" data-start="1611" data-end="1639">
<p data-start="1613" data-end="1639">Upload it back to GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eikcj5" data-start="1640" data-end="1664">
<p data-start="1642" data-end="1664">Turn on GitHub Pages</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dnzm6q" data-start="1665" data-end="1740">
<p data-start="1667" data-end="1677">Use it as:</p>
<ul data-start="1680" data-end="1740">
<li data-section-id="11ixi36" data-start="1680" data-end="1693">
<p data-start="1682" data-end="1693">Portfolio</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="119w68a" data-start="1696" data-end="1714">
<p data-start="1698" data-end="1714">Client website</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i6bd4r" data-start="1717" data-end="1740">
<p data-start="1719" data-end="1740">Fiverr/Upwork proof</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1742" data-end="1745">
<p data-start="1747" data-end="1771">If you want, next I can:</p>
<ul data-start="1772" data-end="1931" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="k557cr" data-start="1772" data-end="1811">
<p data-start="1774" data-end="1811">Help you <strong data-start="1783" data-end="1811">put it live step-by-step</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fvbewq" data-start="1812" data-end="1863">
<p data-start="1814" data-end="1863">Fix your <strong data-start="1823" data-end="1863">design to look like premium law firm</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12pkhlt" data-start="1864" data-end="1931" data-is-last-node="">
