<p data-start="172" data-end="200">Let’s break this properly 👇</p>
<hr data-start="202" data-end="205">
<h2 data-section-id="yunrtx" data-start="207" data-end="254">✅ 1. WhatsApp button (DO THIS — high impact)</h2>
<p data-start="255" data-end="298">This is one of the best things you can add.</p>
<p data-start="300" data-end="309">Use this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="310" data-end="420"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼv">&lt;a</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">href</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"https://wa.me/923XXXXXXXXX"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"whatsapp-btn"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">target</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"_blank"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>  Chat on WhatsApp</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/a&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="422" data-end="431">Style it:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="432" data-end="619"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">whatsapp-btn</span><span> {</span><br><span>  position: </span><span class="ͼq">fixed</span><span>;</span><br><span>  bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  right: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  background: #25D366;</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼq">12</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  text-decoration: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="621" data-end="688">👉 This alone can increase inquiries a lot (especially in Pakistan)</p>
<hr data-start="690" data-end="693">
<h2 data-section-id="zzeg4w" data-start="695" data-end="756">✅ 2. Background image in hero (GOOD idea, but do it right)</h2>
<p data-start="758" data-end="794">Don’t just throw any “lawyer image”.</p>
<p data-start="796" data-end="803">👉 Use:</p>
<ul data-start="804" data-end="880">
<li data-section-id="mmm1yg" data-start="804" data-end="815">
<p data-start="806" data-end="815">Courtroom</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i9yltz" data-start="816" data-end="831">
<p data-start="818" data-end="831">Justice scale</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j6jrs3" data-start="832" data-end="853">
<p data-start="834" data-end="853">Professional office</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xjgf9l" data-start="854" data-end="880">
<p data-start="856" data-end="880">Dark overlay (IMPORTANT)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="882" data-end="890">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="891" data-end="1052"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>  background: </span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">11</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">31</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">58</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.8</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">11</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">31</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">58</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.8</span><span>)),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">'law-bg.jpg'</span><span>);</span><br><span>  background-size: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1054" data-end="1105">👉 The overlay keeps it <strong data-start="1078" data-end="1105">professional + readable</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1107" data-end="1110">
<h2 data-section-id="1vddb8r" data-start="1112" data-end="1170">⚠️ 3. About adding AI feature (here’s the honest truth)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1ixy6jd" data-start="1172" data-end="1214">❌ Don’t add AI just for the sake of it</h3>
<p data-start="1215" data-end="1243">If you add a random chatbot:</p>
<ul data-start="1244" data-end="1331">
<li data-section-id="18ja2zc" data-start="1244" data-end="1280">
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1280">It can give <strong data-start="1258" data-end="1280">wrong legal advice</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19em3qq" data-start="1281" data-end="1312">
<p data-start="1283" data-end="1312">Makes your site look gimmicky</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oxk38w" data-start="1313" data-end="1331">
<p data-start="1315" data-end="1331">Can reduce trust</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1333" data-end="1336">
<h2 data-section-id="1gft523" data-start="1338" data-end="1370">✅ WHEN AI makes sense for YOU</h2>
<p data-start="1372" data-end="1417">Only add AI if it does something useful like:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ovagto" data-start="1419" data-end="1462">Option A: Simple AI Chat (safe version)</h3>
<ul data-start="1463" data-end="1531">
<li data-section-id="pfwqtw" data-start="1463" data-end="1492">
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1492">“Ask basic legal questions”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sdptob" data-start="1493" data-end="1531">
<p data-start="1495" data-end="1531">Add disclaimer: <em data-start="1511" data-end="1531">“Not legal advice”</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1533" data-end="1539">Tools:</p>
<ul data-start="1540" data-end="1623">
<li data-section-id="15bg0k5" data-start="1540" data-end="1581">
<p data-start="1542" data-end="1581"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Tidio</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17wgcs5" data-start="1582" data-end="1623">
<p data-start="1584" data-end="1623"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Crisp</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1625" data-end="1628">
<h3 data-section-id="1tbadb3" data-start="1630" data-end="1670">Option B (BETTER): Smart intake form</h3>
<p data-start="1671" data-end="1694">Instead of AI, do this:</p>
<p data-start="1696" data-end="1703">👉 Ask:</p>
<ul data-start="1704" data-end="1745">
<li data-section-id="1riwgmw" data-start="1704" data-end="1724">
<p data-start="1706" data-end="1724">What type of case?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4udx9i" data-start="1725" data-end="1735">
<p data-start="1727" data-end="1735">Urgency?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17yklpu" data-start="1736" data-end="1745">
<p data-start="1738" data-end="1745">Budget?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1747" data-end="1790">This is <strong data-start="1755" data-end="1790">way more useful than AI chatbot</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1792" data-end="1795">
<h3 data-section-id="1n56l71" data-start="1797" data-end="1844">Option C (Advanced – if you really want AI)</h3>
<ul data-start="1845" data-end="1925">
<li data-section-id="1ssl1do" data-start="1845" data-end="1894">
<p data-start="1847" data-end="1894">AI that drafts legal documents (contracts etc.)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qnszyb" data-start="1895" data-end="1925">
<p data-start="1897" data-end="1925">AI that summarizes case info</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1927" data-end="1973">👉 But this needs backend (not beginner level)</p>
<hr data-start="1975" data-end="1978">
<h2 data-section-id="1bnqhuh" data-start="1980" data-end="2026">🎯 My recommendation for YOU (no confusion)</h2>
<p data-start="2028" data-end="2047">Right now focus on:</p>
<ol data-start="2049" data-end="2163">
<li data-section-id="130g1xt" data-start="2049" data-end="2071">
<p data-start="2052" data-end="2071">✅ WhatsApp button</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ngy7u1" data-start="2072" data-end="2107">
<p data-start="2075" data-end="2107">✅ Hero section with background</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6337v" data-start="2108" data-end="2140">
<p data-start="2111" data-end="2140">✅ Strong services + contact</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ztib6f" data-start="2141" data-end="2163">
<p data-start="2144" data-end="2163">❌ Skip AI for now</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2165" data-end="2168">
<h2 data-section-id="hgan2w" data-start="2170" data-end="2189">💡 Real strategy</h2>
<p data-start="2190" data-end="2233">Your goal is:<br>
👉 Get clients → make money</p>
<p data-start="2235" data-end="2260">Not:<br>
👉 “Cool AI website”</p>
<hr data-start="2262" data-end="2265">
<p data-start="2267" data-end="2296">If you want next step, I can:</p>
<ul data-start="2297" data-end="2447" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="1h5y02d" data-start="2297" data-end="2349">
<p data-start="2299" data-end="2349">Add <strong data-start="2303" data-end="2349">WhatsApp + UI code directly into your site</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tyi14t" data-start="2350" data-end="2387">
<p data-start="2352" data-end="2387">Suggest <strong data-start="2360" data-end="2387">exact background images</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="as3b4r" data-start="2388" data-end="2447" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="2390" data-end="2447" data-is-last-node="">Or design a <strong data-start="2402" data-end="2447" data-is-last-node="">client-converting homepage layout for you</strong></p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-c