<p data-start="73" data-end="225">👉 Your website is live, but it’s just <strong data-start="112" data-end="162">files on <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></strong>.<br data-start="163" data-end="166">
To edit it, you simply modify those files and push updates.</p>
<hr data-start="227" data-end="230">
<h2 data-section-id="1u734en" data-start="232" data-end="270">🚀 EASIEST WAY (No software needed)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1pqa7ur" data-start="272" data-end="301">✅ Edit directly on GitHub</h3>
<ol data-start="303" data-end="520">
<li data-section-id="10mc8pj" data-start="303" data-end="350">
<p data-start="306" data-end="350">Go to your repo:<br data-start="322" data-end="325">
👉 <code data-start="331" data-end="350">ms-law-associates</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1as1wl7" data-start="352" data-end="376">
<p data-start="355" data-end="376">Click on <code data-start="364" data-end="376">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q12tt0" data-start="378" data-end="416">
<p data-start="381" data-end="416">Click the ✏️ <strong data-start="394" data-end="416">Edit (pencil icon)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sz12vo" data-start="418" data-end="477">
<p data-start="421" data-end="477">Make your changes (e.g. add WhatsApp button, text, etc.)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="b2h3vd" data-start="479" data-end="520">
<p data-start="482" data-end="520">Scroll down → click <strong data-start="502" data-end="520">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="522" data-end="525">
<h3 data-section-id="ug6xwr" data-start="527" data-end="541">⏱️ Result:</h3>
<p data-start="542" data-end="591">Your site updates automatically in 10–30 seconds.</p>
<hr data-start="593" data-end="596">
<h2 data-section-id="1v4bf3k" data-start="598" data-end="636">💻 BETTER WAY (Recommended for you)</h2>
<p data-start="638" data-end="679">Use <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Visual Studio Code</span></span></p>
<h3 data-section-id="onac65" data-start="681" data-end="691">Steps:</h3>
<ol data-start="692" data-end="902">
<li data-section-id="r978qr" data-start="692" data-end="767">
<p data-start="695" data-end="767">Download your project (ZIP) from <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ijuck4" data-start="768" data-end="795">
<p data-start="771" data-end="795">Open folder in VS Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sz6h2w" data-start="796" data-end="840">
<p data-start="799" data-end="840">Edit files (<code data-start="811" data-end="823">index.html</code>, <code data-start="825" data-end="837">styles.css</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8dlku0" data-start="841" data-end="867">
<p data-start="844" data-end="867">Test with Live Server</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14d1xtp" data-start="868" data-end="902">
<p data-start="871" data-end="902">Upload changes back to GitHub</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="904" data-end="907">
<h2 data-section-id="4jtmci" data-start="909" data-end="946">🔁 How to upload updated code back</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="104p1lw" data-start="948" data-end="973">Option A (simple way)</h3>
<ul data-start="974" data-end="1051">
<li data-section-id="13l2zcy" data-start="974" data-end="1016">
<p data-start="976" data-end="1016">Go to repo → <strong data-start="989" data-end="1016">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10vzi89" data-start="1017" data-end="1042">
<p data-start="1019" data-end="1042">Drag your updated files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uwjkah" data-start="1043" data-end="1051">
<p data-start="1045" data-end="1051">Commit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1053" data-end="1056">
<h3 data-section-id="jvbhyx" data-start="1058" data-end="1088">Option B (pro way – later)</h3>
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1134">Use Git commands (I’ll teach you when needed)</p>
<hr data-start="1136" data-end="1139">
<h2 data-section-id="1bqxqa8" data-start="1141" data-end="1173">🎯 What YOU should edit first</h2>
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1206">Start with these (high impact):</p>
<h3 data-section-id="kw1x3q" data-start="1208" data-end="1236">1. Add WhatsApp button</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="n8cpmu" data-start="1237" data-end="1262">2. Update Hero text</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="jpf5oz" data-start="1263" data-end="1292">3. Add background image</h3>
<h3 data-section-id="ff44zl" data-start="1293" data-end="1326">4. Improve services section</h3>
<hr data-start="1328" data-end="1331">
<h2 data-section-id="7lag6j" data-start="1333" data-end="1353">⚠️ Common mistake</h2>
<p data-start="1354" data-end="1360">Don’t:</p>
<ul data-start="1361" data-end="1433">
<li data-section-id="1blqj6i" data-start="1361" data-end="1378">
<p data-start="1363" data-end="1378">Edit randomly</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sh7siq" data-start="1379" data-end="1398">
<p data-start="1381" data-end="1398">Break structure</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="159g5cs" data-start="1399" data-end="1433">
<p data-start="1401" data-end="1433">Change too many things at once</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1435" data-end="1471">👉 Do small changes → check → update</p>
<hr data-start="1473" data-end="1476">
<h2 data-section-id="mlqk7q" data-start="1478" data-end="1505">🔥 Best workflow for you</h2>
<ol data-start="1506" data-end="1594">
<li data-section-id="1ksgvyh" data-start="1506" data-end="1526">
<p data-start="1509" data-end="1526">Edit in VS Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="effjiv" data-start="1527" data-end="1544">
<p data-start="1530" data-end="1544">Test locally</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5rdef9" data-start="1545" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1548" data-end="1566">Upload to GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a7kk8e" data-start="1567" data-end="1594">
<p data-start="1570" data-end="1594">Refresh your live site</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1596" data-end="1599">
<h2 data-section-id="t92y18" data-start="1601" data-end="1627">👇 Let’s do it together</h2>
<p data-start="1628" data-end="1636">Tell me:</p>
<p data-start="1638" data-end="1714">👉 “I want to add WhatsApp button”<br data-start="1672" data-end="1675">
or<br data-start="1677" data-end="1680">
👉 “I want to change hero section”</p>
