<ul data-start="232" data-end="278">
<li data-section-id="182ob27" data-start="232" data-end="253">
<p data-start="234" data-end="253">Dark background ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qq9d0u" data-start="254" data-end="278">
<p data-start="256" data-end="278">Gold/bronze statue ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="280" data-end="313">👉 That’s PERFECT for your theme.</p>
<hr data-start="315" data-end="318">
<h2 data-section-id="62qtbd" data-start="320" data-end="358">✅ Step 1: Add it as Hero Background</h2>
<p data-start="360" data-end="422">Put the image in your project folder (e.g. name it <code data-start="411" data-end="421">hero.jpg</code>)</p>
<p data-start="424" data-end="450">Then in your <code data-start="437" data-end="449">styles.css</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="452" data-end="689"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>  background: </span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">11</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">31</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">58</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.85</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">11</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">31</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">58</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.85</span><span>)),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">'hero.jpg'</span><span>);</span><br><span>  background-size: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>  background-position: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼq">120</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="691" data-end="694">
<h2 data-section-id="14r8wpb" data-start="696" data-end="716">🔥 Why this works</h2>
<ul data-start="717" data-end="870">
<li data-section-id="luybro" data-start="717" data-end="781">
<p data-start="719" data-end="781">The <strong data-start="723" data-end="744">dark blue overlay</strong> (rgba 11,31,58) matches your theme</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s4gszf" data-start="782" data-end="840">
<p data-start="784" data-end="840">It removes brightness → makes it look <strong data-start="822" data-end="838">professional</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1aivtr6" data-start="841" data-end="870">
<p data-start="843" data-end="870">Text becomes easy to read</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="872" data-end="875">
<h2 data-section-id="1pa243d" data-start="877" data-end="912">✅ Step 2: Make text look premium</h2>
<p data-start="914" data-end="923">Add this:</p>
