<hr data-start="1284" data-end="1287">
<h2 data-section-id="yeb0u1" data-start="1289" data-end="1322">⚠️ Common mistake (avoid this)</h2>
<ul data-start="1323" data-end="1457">
<li data-section-id="1mrndke" data-start="1323" data-end="1371">
<p data-start="1325" data-end="1371">❌ Bright image without overlay → looks cheap</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="u40kcv" data-start="1372" data-end="1410">
<p data-start="1374" data-end="1410">❌ Random stock image → kills trust</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="adsu3p" data-start="1411" data-end="1457">
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1457">❌ Too zoomed or pixelated → unprofessional</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1459" data-end="1462">
<h2 data-section-id="1xnhy3g" data-start="1464" data-end="1491">🎯 Final Result You Want</h2>
