</li>
<li data-section-id="1orpmkq" data-start="1517" data-end="1549">
<p data-start="1519" data-end="1549">Golden statue subtly visible</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rcd8sd" data-start="1550" data-end="1577">
<p data-start="1552" data-end="1577">Clean white text on top</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tj90p5" data-start="1578" data-end="1597">
<p data-start="1580" data-end="1597">Gold button (CTA)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1599" data-end="1646">👉 That combination = <strong data-start="1621" data-end="1646">premium law firm look</strong></p>
