rkdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="53">Good eye—that mismatch breaks the whole premium feel.</p>
<p data-start="55" data-end="171">👉 Problem: Your <strong data-start="72" data-end="137">“Danyal Durrani – Tax Expert” card is not structured the same</strong> as the others.<br data-start="152" data-end="155">
