<p data-start="122" data-end="235">👉 What happened:<br data-start="139" data-end="142">
When we changed your card, we <strong data-start="172" data-end="209">broke the original HTML structure</strong> that your CSS depends on.</p>
<hr data-start="237" data-end="240">
<h1 data-section-id="1921o1l" data-start="242" data-end="287">🎯 FIX (restore original structure exactly)</h1>
<p data-start="289" data-end="343">We need to make your card <strong data-start="315" data-end="328">IDENTICAL</strong> to the others.</p>
<hr data-start="345" data-end="348">
