<hr data-start="762" data-end="765">
<h2 data-section-id="np8iyl" data-start="767" data-end="797">✅ Step 2: Connect it in CSS</h2>
<p data-start="799" data-end="826">Make sure your <code data-start="814" data-end="821">.hero</code> has:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="828" data-end="940"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-d25c669f.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼv">background</span><span>:</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼs">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼs">rgba</span><span>(11,31,58,0.9), </span><span class="ͼs">rgba</span><span>(11,31,58,0.9)),</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">'hero.jpg'</span><span>);</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="942" data-end="945">
<h1 data-section-id="1tltl2q" data-start="947" data-end="967">⚠️ Important rules</h1>
<ul data-start="968" data-end="1093">
<li data-section-id="1rwe5sz" data-start="968" data-end="1018">
<p data-start="970" data-end="1018">Image must be in <strong data-start="987" data-end="1016">same folder as index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ustlr8" data-start="1019" data-end="1058">
<p data-start="1021" data-end="1058">Name must match exactly: <code data-start="1046" data-end="1056">hero.jpg</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qf4v5t" data-start="1059" data-end="1093">
<p data-start="1061" data-end="1093">Don’t use bright/random images</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1095" data-end="1098">
<h1 data-section-id="rt57z4" data-start="1100" data-end="1140">🔥 If you DON’T want to use that image</h1>
<p data-start="1142" data-end="1179">Tell me:<br>
👉 “give me best background”</p>
<p data-start="1181" data-end="1195">I’ll give you:</p>
<ul data-start="1196" data-end="1291">
<li data-section-id="vlczvf" data-start="1196" data-end="1223">
<p data-start="1198" data-end="1223">Exact image suggestions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12vrcue" data-start="1224" data-end="1253">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1253">Matching your color theme</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sphbwv" data-start="1254" data-end="1291">
<p data-start="1256" data-end="1291">Professional (not cheap stock look)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1293" data-end="1296">
<h1 data-section-id="7eqdmp" data-start="1298" data-end="1316">🎯 Final clarity</h1>
<p data-start="1317" data-end="1366">👉 The background is NOT automatic<br data-start="1351" data-end="1354">
👉 You must:</p>
<ul data-start="1367" data-end="1402">
<li data-section-id="73slu4" data-start="1367" data-end="1383">
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1383">Upload image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mpe8oh" data-start="1384" data-end="1402">
<p data-start="1386" data-end="1402">Link it in CSS</p>
</li>
</ul>
