If you don’t like the statue image, <strong data-start="80" data-end="98">don’t force it</strong>. The goal is <em data-start="112" data-end="129">premium + clean</em>, not “legal cliché”.</p>
<hr data-start="152" data-end="155">
<h1 data-section-id="1bxq2my" data-start="157" data-end="214">🎯 BEST BACKGROUND OPTIONS (for your navy + gold theme)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1n0xn" data-start="216" data-end="273">🔥 Option 1 (RECOMMENDED): Dark Abstract / Office Blur</h2>
<p data-start="274" data-end="314">👉 This is what top law firms use today.</p>
<p data-start="316" data-end="329"><strong data-start="316" data-end="329">Look for:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="330" data-end="426">
<li data-section-id="1g9i2wi" data-start="330" data-end="360">
<p data-start="332" data-end="360">Dark navy/black background</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s6ccu6" data-start="361" data-end="404">
<p data-start="363" data-end="404">Slight blur (office, desk, city lights)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="isvipb" data-start="405" data-end="426">
<p data-start="407" data-end="426">Minimal, not busy</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="428" data-end="445"><strong data-start="428" data-end="445">Why it works:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="446" data-end="531">
<li data-section-id="syduvk" data-start="446" data-end="469">
<p data-start="448" data-end="469">Keeps focus on text</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15o6kiv" data-start="470" data-end="498">
<p data-start="472" data-end="498">Looks modern + expensive</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1eqhduz" data-start="499" data-end="531">
<p data-start="501" data-end="531">Matches your theme perfectly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="533" data-end="536">
<h2 data-section-id="anevtu" data-start="538" data-end="580">⚖️ Option 2: Modern Law Office Interior</h2>
<p data-start="581" data-end="614">👉 Not courtroom—<strong data-start="598" data-end="614">clean office</strong></p>
<p data-start="616" data-end="629"><strong data-start="616" data-end="629">Look for:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="630" data-end="694">
<li data-section-id="7ixtiw" data-start="630" data-end="653">
<p data-start="632" data-end="653">Wooden desk + books</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1u8cof3" data-start="654" data-end="671">
<p data-start="656" data-end="671">Warm lighting</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6y8ue4" data-start="672" data-end="694">
<p data-start="674" data-end="694">Slightly dark tone</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="696" data-end="706"><strong data-start="696" data-end="706">Avoid:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="707" data-end="762">
<li data-section-id="mm9n7l" data-start="707" data-end="732">
<p data-start="709" data-end="732">Bright white office ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wcj8a0" data-start="733" data-end="762">
<p data-start="735" data-end="762">Cartoonish stock images ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="764" data-end="767">
<h2 data-section-id="5uy12r" data-start="769" data-end="818">🏙️ Option 3: Dark City Skyline (Very Premium)</h2>
<p data-start="819" data-end="849">👉 Used by corporate law firms</p>
<p data-start="851" data-end="864"><strong data-start="851" data-end="864">Look for:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="865" data-end="927">
<li data-section-id="w9thz0" data-start="865" data-end="887">
<p data-start="867" data-end="887">Night city skyline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m2rj99" data-start="888" data-end="908">
<p data-start="890" data-end="908">Blue/black tones</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rl2yau" data-start="909" data-end="927">
<p data-start="911" data-end="927">Minimal lights</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="929" data-end="932">
<h1 data-section-id="1uk2em" data-start="934" data-end="951">❌ WHAT TO AVOID</h1>
<ul data-start="952" data-end="1097">
<li data-section-id="xtkqia" data-start="952" data-end="1000">
<p data-start="954" data-end="1000">Lady Justice statue (if you don’t like it) ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1op7kg1" data-start="1001" data-end="1045">
<p data-start="1003" data-end="1045">Gavel close-ups ❌ (overused, cheap feel)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fre60g" data-start="1046" data-end="1074">
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1074">Bright colorful images ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="195xqas" data-start="1075" data-end="1097">
<p data-start="1077" data-end="1097">Busy backgrounds ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1099" data-end="1102">
<h1 data-section-id="1wme8zn" data-start="1104" data-end="1141">🎯 MY STRONG RECOMMENDATION FOR YOU</h1>
<p data-start="1143" data-end="1185">👉 Use: <strong data-start="1151" data-end="1185">Dark blurred office background</strong></p>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1198">This gives:</p>
<ul data-start="1199" data-end="1266">
<li data-section-id="1osorel" data-start="1199" data-end="1222">
<p data-start="1201" data-end="1222">Professional feel ✔</p>
