<hr data-start="156" data-end="159">
<h1 data-section-id="1rrckmr" data-start="161" data-end="201">🔥 BEST BACKGROUND STYLE (Recommended)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="u3dzyw" data-start="203" data-end="246">🧑‍💼 Dark Office / Corporate Background</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="zm51is" data-start="249" data-end="287">Why this is PERFECT for your site:</h3>
<ul data-start="288" data-end="437">
<li data-section-id="1u211gu" data-start="288" data-end="331">
<p data-start="290" data-end="331">Dark tones = <strong data-start="303" data-end="329">professional + serious</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="315p88" data-start="332" data-end="373">
